title: BIW Master Course
short_desc: BIW is brief for Body in White that is a step in automotive design and manufacturing. BIW refers to the body shell design of an automotive product such as cars. It is just a sheet metal welded structure. BIW will not have doors, engines, chassis or any other moving parts. At Excellence Techno vision, you can have the best BIW training in Sign venture.
